videos.headline: Buffalo's Jackson throws deep strike for for a 33-yard TD
videos.description: Buffalo's Tyree Jackson floats a deep throw to an open Charlie Jones for a 33-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Terry Jr. scorches Temple defense for 22-yard TD
videos.description: Buffalo's Tim Terry Jr. gets the handoff and finds his way through Temple's defense for a 22-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Temple gets on board with a 39-yard TD before the half
videos.description: Tample's Frank Nutile winds up and launches a deep ball to a leaping Branden Mack for a 39-yard touchdown

videos.headline: Temple'goes up on 44-yard TD pass
videos.description: A Frank Nutile 44-yard touchdown pass to Randle Jones gives Temple a lead over Buffalo.

videos.headline: Temple ties game with blocked-punt TD and crazy reverse 2-point-conversion
videos.description: Temple recovers a blocked punt in the end zone and then ties the game with a nice reverse pass for a 2-point conversion.
